    Wait what did you say? BDSM? What is that? Some sort of UNIX alternative? Let's just ignore that and keep talking about keyboards.<br />
    <br />
    After a couple hours of tutorials <i>(jk I just made it up on the spot)</i> and a handful of minutes tying up <i>some loose ends</i>, this is the final product:
    <br />
</p>
